ilures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,250],"id":"12ef93f4-2f11-0b99-2708-b10e2183e4d2","name":"Note: Process 'standard' → Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,760],"id":"e4303ab1-9488-6cb3-cab8-b0b28edd01bd","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1270],"id":"6abf3a9c-ec59-4eef-0970-a92f1c20523d","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1780],"id":"f218abf3-bff4-1aae-d1c3-14257ec54384","name":"Note: Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Routed Work\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"33ac093f-ac71-0f5f-84ed-63752b11f9a1","name":"Note: Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"16b36a75-a58b-29ee-39b5-f9b92c72032f","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"cf132339-1650-280f-a939-a0cc12b45c7c","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"b6055617-3f01-07fe-09c2-047bd3b1bd5c","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Enrich with Reference Data · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"4287125d-c496-439a-b363-1f8d3e0304e1","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"22131c6e-cb98-cd18-c454-b2dc5ab0cc85","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"dbfbad86-e9ef-a1ef-d98e-9915d7d50f80","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"67ad8b49-6f77-ff23-dcdc-3f1462974d49","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Gmail · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"d8cb84b4-3b88-7401-7797-de45d2b1ebef","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Gmail\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"facba1dc-f6ba-cc19-fa8d-d3f6ff05e9f5","name":"Note: Send Summary to Gmail"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,1540],"id":"b12185d9-dcca-8083-d88a-5846dab29cfa","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,1540],"id":"eebc9a44-d005-9996-48f3-2ef888fea1c8","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,1540],"id":"84e02b56-99da-a4e7-bc35-68f420975760","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Capture applications with Notion and Gmail for your team\n\n**Pattern:** Form Intake · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nCapture applications with Notion and Gmail for your team. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual inbox triage is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Email Form Submission → Normalize Email Payload → Route by Work Type → Process 'standard' → Google Sheets → Merge Routed Work → Load Previous Snapshot → Compute Drift vs Snapshot → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to form intake without manual effort\n- Anyone automating inbox triage in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Scales without extra headcount\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"68e98707-85a2-1c84-e8e7-562c36c80f45","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"8ec03b92-bf53-c5d0-d9ae-d2a0640a108b","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your inbox triage process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"a33f818d-066e-4037-18b3-c5456e0fbf75","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Email Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Email Payload","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Email Payload":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Work Type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Work Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Process 'standard' → Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Process 'standard' → Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Routed Work":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Gmail","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Gmail":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"set